snippet.title: Uncharted Waters Online | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Begin your journey in Europe and then to the rest of the world as a voyager during the Age of Discovery! Sail the seas in this open-world MMORPG sandbox as who you want and how you want with your trusty ship.

Set sail today!
https://uwo.papayaplay.com/uwo.do?tp=game

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/gaming/OfficialUnchartedWaters
Twitter: https://twitter.com/UWO_News
